{"tid":1569221,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"無線充比有線更快？小米發佈 30W超級無線閃充","createTime":"2019-09-14T14:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T18:53:53.000Z","uid":7828,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb68a36947153a95fc5953a7ad73d2ef6aa0a8f","tid":1569221,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:03:05.000Z","msg":"小米在早些年的智能手機充電速度上飽受詬病，好在近年，小米手機的充電速度越來越快，甚至在無線充電的功率上取得了世界最高水平。在小米先前的預告中，給我們公佈了全新的「Mi Charge Turbo」充電技術。小米稱這一個新技術可以實現無線充電速度超越有線充電，引來了大家的推測。<br />\n<br />\n日前，小米不再藏頭露了，直接正式公佈「小米超級無線閃充」技術，稱其無線充電的功率是30W，這個充電技術比市面上大多數旗艦手機還快。<br />\n<br />\n上一代的小米無線充電技術達到了20W，這一次甚至直接提升到了30W，成為了全世界功率最高的無線充電技術。據稱只需要69分鐘就可以充滿 4000mAh 電池，而 25分鐘就可以充到50% 。並且還擁有反向高速快充，在 30分鐘內將 iPhone XS 充電20%，比華為 P30 Pro 在相同時間內可充 ​​iPhone XS 到13%。<br />\n<br />\n對於新一代「Mi Charge Turbo」，小米會先運用在哪一款機型上呢？小米這一次也不含糊，直接說會首先搭載在小米9 Pro 5G 這款 5G 旗艦手機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n針對小米的無線快充技術，華為也有相應的舉動。華為稱 30W無線充電在8月通過了FCC 認證，代表著很快就會推出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/technology/player?newsId=362396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Ftechnology%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362396&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=33393ed0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Ftechnology%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362396&h=85f217b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/technology/player?newsId=362396</a>"},{"pid":"1a65cfb0676119eaf8fc4b90b6d9a64ba08e954d","tid":1569221,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:05:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f942799bfb1ddea45432d8524c52a4c6ba10256c","tid":1569221,"uid":201414,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:05:39.000Z","msg":"又借啲意吹奏支那 祝樓主老母被支那狗屌到屎忽開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36e4ed74b501447aa5d15ac76e9925a6f125243","tid":1569221,"uid":281342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y31tg5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy31tg5b.jpg&h=af101f74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LPoZ8bS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLPoZ8bS.jpg&h=25b70c67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"337e5d7d771b42f945cc71d6ab9ebb763b00dd18","tid":1569221,"uid":22288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:53:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}